Overview:
The 3D Calculator is an interactive and visually enhanced calculator application designed with a three-dimensional user interface to provide a more engaging user experience. Unlike traditional flat calculators, this project integrates depth, shadows, and perspective styling using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript (or Tkinter for desktop) to simulate a 3D effect.

